 Surface: Hayden Marquard\n   3. ☒ Calorimetry: (asked Reika [2026-06-18 Th
 u])\n7. ☐ *Equipment status*:\n   1. light scattering\n   2. electron micr
 oscopy\n   3. rheology\n   4. ☐ x-ray\n   5. ☐ surface analysis / contact 
 angle\n   6. ☐ *calorimetry*: TGA\, DSC\n8. ☐ *Review handouts*
